These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade, coffee, cola, water
The people have 5 different jobs:  watercher, police-officer, software-developer, librarian, architect
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: gospel, r&b, indie, dubstep, classical
There are 5 different nationalities: japanese, german, malaysian, french, chinese
 1. the malaysian is on the left or right of the architect##3
 2. the watercher is in an odd position##4
 3. the fan of gospel is on the left of the german##1
 4. the person drinking water is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
 5. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the watercher##3
 6. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 7. the architect is on the right of the fan of indie##1
 8. the chinese is in an even position##4
 9. the japanese is on the left or right of the librarian##3
10. the fan of indie is the software-developer##1
11. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
12. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the watercher##3
13. the person drinking water is on the right of the german##1
14. the chinese is on the left of the fan of classical##1
15. the fan of dubstep is the person drinking cola##1
16. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |        2        |     3      |    4     |     5     |
| Beverage      | coffee    | 7up   | cola     | water      | lemonade      |
| Job           | software-developer | architect | watercher    | librarian | police-officer |
| Music-Genre   | indie       | gospel         | dubstep      | r&b      | classical    |
| Nationality   | malaysian    | french         | german | chinese  | japanese   |

