.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: puzzles, baking, chess, traveling, rock-climbing
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: jazz, r&b, metal, house, hip-hop
5 different pets are kept: bird, pony, cat, fish, dog
The people use 5 different means of transport: train, helicopter, bike, tram, car
 1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
 2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
 3. the person who's hobby is chess is the fan of hip-hop##1
 4. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 5. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 6. the fan of metal is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
 8. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person driving the train##2
 9. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
10. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##3
11. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the train##1
12. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
13. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
14. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |      5      |
| Hobby         | traveling | baking | chess   | puzzles | rock-climbing |
| Music-Genre   | metal      | r&b   | hip-hop    | jazz        | house        |
| Pet           | fish         | dog  | bird  | pony   | cat      |
| Transport     | train        | tram  | bike | car | helicopter         |

