.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-3::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, sprite, iced-tea, 7up
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: thriller, satire, documentary, epic, romance
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: cricket, lacrosse, rowing, cycling, skateboarding
The people use 5 different means of transport: snowmobile, airplane, motorbike, ship, van
 1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
 3. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 5. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 6. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far right##1
 8. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
 9. the person watching epic movies is the person driving the motorbike##1
10. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
11. the person driving the ship is the person drinking 7up##1
12. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the person driving the airplane and the person watching thriller movies##2
13. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
14. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far left or far right##3
15. the person drinking 7up is in an odd position##4
16. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3     |      4       |       5       |
| Beverage      | 7up       | almond-milk   | cola    | iced-tea     | sprite |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller     | satire   | documentary   | epic | romance       |
| Sport         | skateboarding | lacrosse | cricket | cycling     | rowing        |
| Transport     | ship       | snowmobile     | airplane  | motorbike   | van         |

