.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-4::.
There 5 different types of food: garlic, peas, mango, lettuce, apricot
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: romance, adventure, mystery, family, sports
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: rock, trance, gospel, disco, indie
The people use 5 different means of transport: roller, taxi, car, jet-ski, motorbike
 1. the person driving the taxi is between the person watching mystery movies and the person driving the roller##2
 2. the person watching family movies is on the far right##1
 3. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person eating peas##1
 4. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4
 5. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
 6. the person driving the motorbike is the person eating garlic##1
 7. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 8. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
 9. the person eating apricot is the fan of indie##1
10. the person watching adventure movies is in an odd position##4
11. the fan of disco is on the far left##1
12. the person driving the roller is on the far left or far right##3
13. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
14. the person eating garlic is the person eating garlic##1
15. the person driving the jet-ski is the person watching sports movies##1
16. the person eating mango is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
17. the person eating lettuce is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |     5      |
