 8. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person driving the subway##2
 9. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
10. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
11. the person driving the jet-ski is the malaysian##1
12. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
13. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's sport is sailing##1
14. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
15. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the malaysian##1
