.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-7::.
There 5 different types of food: lime, broccoli, plum, pumpkin, tomato
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: drama, disaster, western, family, action
5 different pets are kept: goldfish, rabbit, turtle, fish, bird
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: climbing, volleyball, snowboarding, ice-hockey, baseball
 1. the person eating pumpkin is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 2. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
 3. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
 4. the person eating plum is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left##1
 6. the owner of the rabbit is between the person who's sport is baseball and the owner of the bird##2
 7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the owner of the fish##2
 8. the owner of the turtle is the owner of the turtle##1
 9. the person eating broccoli is the person who's sport is climbing##1
10. the person eating lime is in the middle##1
11. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
12. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
13. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
14. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
15. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
16. the person watching family movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
