 3. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
 4. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
 5. the japanese is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an even position##4
 7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
 8. the owner of the mouse is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person eating kale##2
 9. the mexican is on the right of the nigerian##1
10. the mexican is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
11. the mexican is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far right##1
13. the person eating banana is on the far right##1
14. the person eating kale is on the far left or far right##3
15. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3

.:: Answer ::.
